---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Cloudflare Platform Showcase">
  <p class="mb-4">This mini-site demonstrates multiple Cloudflare edge capabilities deployed on <code>andreysergeevich.me</code>.</p>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
    <li>KV-backed visit counter (<code>/visits</code>)</li>
    <li>D1 + Turnstile guestbook (<code>/guestbook</code>)</li>
    <li>Geo introspection (<code>/geo-test</code>)</li>
    <li>R2 listing (<code>/r2</code>)</li>
    <li>Queues / Durable Objects (scaffolding placeholders)</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-6 text-sm opacity-70">Fill in bindings via <code>wrangler-andrey.toml</code> & create resources before showcasing.</p>
</BaseLayout>
